The paper discusses a method for retrieving relevant queries in the context of community question answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories in computer science, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Computation and Language (cs.CC). Among these, cs.IR is the most likely category as the paper focuses on ranking and retrieval of relevant queries. The other categories are also relevant as they involve similar techniques and applications.
